author: Cleo Abram
description:
Did you know the Earth was spinning faster this summer?  This is a big deal, because lots of things depend on us knowing precisely where the earth is.

Turns out there are 3 main things that can change Earth’s spin… 

To learn more optimistic science and technology, subscribe!

title: Why Earth Spun Faster This Summer
